         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">31/10/81 ¶  ¶ You were so good, dear Mr Ramsay, to send me some months ago a fucaceous plant, dredged by you from a depth of 40-60 feet in Port Jackson. ¶  As there were  ¶ no ¶   ¶ fruits ¶  on your ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">81.10.31</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">ML MSS.562, Letters to E. P. Ramsay 1862-91, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">31/10/81<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">3 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">over</seg> 2 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">(or possibly </seg>2 <seg style="font-style: italic; ">over </seg>3<seg style="font-style: italic; ">)</seg>.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You were so good, dear Mr Ramsay, to send me some months ago a fucaceous plant, dredged by you from a depth of 40-60 feet in Port Jackson.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sydney.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> As there were <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">no</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">fruits</hi>
               </seg> on your specimens, I sent them to Dr Sonder, the great Algologist with whom I am in correspondence on Algs for more than 30 years! <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">He</hi>
               </seg> also can make nothing of it, but thinks with me, that it may be a <name key="Sargassum">Sargassum</name>. Will you kindly show these fragments also to the excellent Mr Hasswell,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. A. Haswell.</p>
               </note> who — while dredging — does keep as a rule like you also any Algs for me. Could not for a trifling payment, which I would refund, parties living on different parts of the coast of N.SW. be induced to bring up fresh after a storm a <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">cart</hi>
               </seg>-load full of various Algs (<seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">all</hi>
               </seg> sorts, <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">some</hi>
               </seg> specimens of each), throw them on the floor of a barn or shed for drying, turn them over once a day, put them when quite dry in a corn bag and forward them with account of expenses. Such algae must <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">not</hi>
               </seg> be washed in fresh water!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>N.S.W. stands very poorly <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in the Census of Algs as yet.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Got the additional fruits of your palm.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Sargassum">Sargassum</name>
            </p>
